INSERT INTO `sl_blogs` (`id`, `title`, `titlefr`, `titlesp`, `title_french`, `image`, `description`, `description_front`, `description_front_french`, `description_front_spanish`, `status`, `slug`, `slugfr`, `CreatedAt`, `UpdatedAt`) VALUES
(27, 'OZEETY, The FLASHMONI Blockchain on live mode soon!', 'OZEETY, La Blockchain FLASHMONI bientôt en mode live !', '¡OZEETY, The FLASHMONI Blockchain en modo en vivo pronto!', 'OZEETY, La Blockchain FLASHMONI bientôt en mode live !', 'https://lunar-estate.com/serge/admin-panel/upload/blog/1656395356-image_19_1.png', '&lt;p&gt;In an era of technological transformations at every level of our day to day life, we are creating a distributed ledger solution to meet with today&amp;rsquo;s problems for most financial clients and users. In doing so, we explored all the possible solutions in the market in terms of financial services, Blockchain technologies, banking wallet and security solutions for all transactions and make it easy for our clients and partners.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Following detailed studies and being responsible for our clients&amp;rsquo; financial matters, as well as the growth of the company and clients&amp;rsquo; needs, we created our own blockchain, coin, token and digital wallet that will incorporate multiple bank accounts (both Fiat and Crypto), thinking of our modern necessities. When it comes to our finances, we all want to have security, fast transactions and pay lower or no fees than we currently do use traditional banking and even modern wallets, exchanges and payment solutions. In trying to achieve this, the problem and solution became a greater challenge, but you will be pleased to know that we never gave up the challenge. Our aim is building something that addressed the &amp;ldquo;financial vision and beyond&amp;rdquo;. Our mantra.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flashmoni blockchain&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://media-exp2.licdn.com/dms/image/C5612AQG6vQoNVWXHMw/article-inline_image-shrink_1500_2232/0/1548963402827?e=1661990400&amp;amp;v=beta&amp;amp;t=kyqiLAHDj4yXe8b96CSKJbrbqA6YZf62a8Z5Pf6Rf94&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The most popular way to release our DApp is on established blockchain platforms like Ethereum, BTC or EOS etc., but the problem is that every blockchain has technical trade-offs, bottlenecks, and constraints. What happens to a DApp that cannot perform due to the limitations of the blockchain they are using?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Bitcoin and Ethereum blockchains are already struggling to meet the traffic, transaction speeds, block sizes and cost of the transaction. Hence, once again we evaluated most of the popular relevant blockchains versus our requirements. The key needs we had were scalability, cost of the transaction, the speed of transaction, security, stable pricing, efficiency, rewards systems, data structure, and consensus algorithm etc.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;So our objective was to address how several of these existing solutions and applications would be suitable for the Flashmoni Ecosystem. In short, it didn&amp;rsquo;t cut it for us and our target key needs, as highlighted above. Building a custom blockchain, or forking a current one, could potentially be a solution to our problem.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;However, nobody knows our business better than we do, so if we build a blockchain that can specifically fit our needs, it can help us be more effective and efficient in managing our business. We started this journey and decided to build our own blockchain due to the following reasons:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot; Choice of the consensus algorithm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot; Choice of programming language&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot; Control of codebase&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot; Ability to update how and whenever you want&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;middot; Ultimate true flexibility and speed at much-reduced costs and fees.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We are launching our own coin, as well as our own currency and investment platform. Why? Because the previous ERC20 was token and there is a huge difference between Coin and Token! Coin operates independently, while token has a specific use in the project&amp;rsquo;s ecosystem, so both have their own role and utility. We are an asset-pegged coin, which is a differentiator between us and majority of the cryptocurrencies existent at the present moment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '<p>In an era of technological transformations at every level of our day to day life, we are creating a distributed ledger solution to meet with today&rsquo;s problems for most financial clients and users. In doing so, we explored all the possible solutions in the market in terms of financial services, Blockchain technologies, banking wallet and security solutions for all transactions and make it easy for our clients and partners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Following detailed studies and being responsible for our clients&rsquo; financial matters, as well as the growth of the company and clients&rsquo; needs, we created our own blockchain, coin, token and digital wallet that will incorporate multiple bank accounts (both Fiat and Crypto), thinking of our modern necessities. When it comes to our finances, we all want to have security, fast transactions and pay lower or no fees than we currently do use traditional banking and even modern wallets, exchanges and payment solutions. In trying to achieve this, the problem and solution became a greater challenge, but you will be pleased to know that we never gave up the challenge. Our aim is building something that addressed the &ldquo;financial vision and beyond&rdquo;. Our mantra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Flashmoni blockchain</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://media-exp2.licdn.com/dms/image/C5612AQG6vQoNVWXHMw/article-inline_image-shrink_1500_2232/0/1548963402827?e=1661990400&amp;v=beta&amp;t=kyqiLAHDj4yXe8b96CSKJbrbqA6YZf62a8Z5Pf6Rf94\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most popular way to release our DApp is on established blockchain platforms like Ethereum, BTC or EOS etc., but the problem is that every blockchain has technical trade-offs, bottlenecks, and constraints. What happens to a DApp that cannot perform due to the limitations of the blockchain they are using?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Bitcoin and Ethereum blockchains are already struggling to meet the traffic, transaction speeds, block sizes and cost of the transaction. Hence, once again we evaluated most of the popular relevant blockchains versus our requirements. The key needs we had were scalability, cost of the transaction, the speed of transaction, security, stable pricing, efficiency, rewards systems, data structure, and consensus algorithm etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So our objective was to address how several of these existing solutions and applications would be suitable for the Flashmoni Ecosystem. In short, it didn&rsquo;t cut it for us and our target key needs, as highlighted above. Building a custom blockchain, or forking a current one, could potentially be a solution to our problem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, nobody knows our business better than we do, so if we build a blockchain that can specifically fit our needs, it can help us be more effective and efficient in managing our business. We started this journey and decided to build our own blockchain due to the following reasons:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Choice of the consensus algorithm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Choice of programming language</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Control of codebase</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Ability to update how and whenever you want</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Ultimate true flexibility and speed at much-reduced costs and fees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are launching our own coin, as well as our own currency and investment platform. Why? Because the previous ERC20 was token and there is a huge difference between Coin and Token! Coin operates independently, while token has a specific use in the project&rsquo;s ecosystem, so both have their own role and utility. We are an asset-pegged coin, which is a differentiator between us and majority of the cryptocurrencies existent at the present moment.</p>\r\n', '<p>&Agrave; une &eacute;poque de transformations technologiques &agrave; tous les niveaux de notre vie quotidienne, nous cr&eacute;ons une solution de registre distribu&eacute; pour r&eacute;pondre aux probl&egrave;mes actuels de la plupart des clients et utilisateurs financiers. Ce faisant, nous avons explor&eacute; toutes les solutions possibles sur le march&eacute; en termes de services financiers, de technologies Blockchain, de portefeuille bancaire et de solutions de s&eacute;curit&eacute; pour toutes les transactions et nous facilitons la t&acirc;che &agrave; nos clients et partenaires.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s des &eacute;tudes d&eacute;taill&eacute;es et &eacute;tant responsables des questions financi&egrave;res de nos clients, ainsi que de la croissance de l&#39;entreprise et des besoins des clients, nous avons cr&eacute;&eacute; notre propre blockchain, coin, token et portefeuille num&eacute;rique qui int&eacute;grera plusieurs comptes bancaires (Fiat et Crypto) , en pensant &agrave; nos n&eacute;cessit&eacute;s modernes. En ce qui concerne nos finances, nous voulons tous avoir la s&eacute;curit&eacute;, des transactions rapides et payer des frais inf&eacute;rieurs ou nuls &agrave; ceux que nous utilisons actuellement avec les services bancaires traditionnels et m&ecirc;me les portefeuilles, les &eacute;changes et les solutions de paiement modernes. En essayant d&#39;y parvenir, le probl&egrave;me et la solution sont devenus un plus grand d&eacute;fi, mais vous serez heureux de savoir que nous n&#39;avons jamais abandonn&eacute; le d&eacute;fi. Notre objectif est de construire quelque chose qui aborde la &laquo; vision financi&egrave;re et au-del&agrave; &raquo;. Notre mantra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Blockchain Flashmoni</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le moyen le plus populaire de publier notre DApp est sur des plates-formes de blockchain &eacute;tablies comme Ethereum, BTC ou EOS, etc., mais le probl&egrave;me est que chaque blockchain a des compromis techniques, des goulots d&#39;&eacute;tranglement et des contraintes. Qu&#39;advient-il d&#39;un DApp qui ne peut pas fonctionner en raison des limitations de la blockchain qu&#39;il utilise ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les blockchains Bitcoin et Ethereum ont d&eacute;j&agrave; du mal &agrave; r&eacute;pondre au trafic, aux vitesses de transaction, &agrave; la taille des blocs et au co&ucirc;t de la transaction. Par cons&eacute;quent, une fois de plus, nous avons &eacute;valu&eacute; la plupart des cha&icirc;nes de blocs pertinentes populaires par rapport &agrave; nos exigences. Les principaux besoins que nous avions &eacute;taient l&#39;&eacute;volutivit&eacute;, le co&ucirc;t de la transaction, la rapidit&eacute; de la transaction, la s&eacute;curit&eacute;, la stabilit&eacute; des prix, l&#39;efficacit&eacute;, les syst&egrave;mes de r&eacute;compenses, la structure des donn&eacute;es et l&#39;algorithme de consensus, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Notre objectif &eacute;tait donc de d&eacute;terminer comment plusieurs de ces solutions et applications existantes seraient adapt&eacute;es &agrave; l&#39;&eacute;cosyst&egrave;me Flashmoni. En bref, cela n&#39;a pas suffi pour nous et nos besoins cl&eacute;s cibles, comme indiqu&eacute; ci-dessus. Construire une blockchain personnalis&eacute;e, ou cr&eacute;er une blockchain actuelle, pourrait potentiellement &ecirc;tre une solution &agrave; notre probl&egrave;me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cependant, personne ne conna&icirc;t mieux notre entreprise que nous, donc si nous construisons une blockchain qui peut r&eacute;pondre sp&eacute;cifiquement &agrave; nos besoins, cela peut nous aider &agrave; &ecirc;tre plus efficaces et efficients dans la gestion de notre entreprise. Nous avons commenc&eacute; ce voyage et avons d&eacute;cid&eacute; de construire notre propre blockchain pour les raisons suivantes :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Choix de l&#39;algorithme de consensus</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Choix du langage de programmation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Contr&ocirc;le de la base de code</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Possibilit&eacute; de mettre &agrave; jour comment et quand vous le souhaitez</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Flexibilit&eacute; et rapidit&eacute; ultimes &agrave; des co&ucirc;ts et des frais tr&egrave;s r&eacute;duits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous lan&ccedil;ons notre propre pi&egrave;ce, ainsi que notre propre plateforme de devises et d&#39;investissement. Pourquoi? Parce que le pr&eacute;c&eacute;dent ERC20 &eacute;tait symbolique et qu&#39;il y a une &eacute;norme diff&eacute;rence entre Coin et Token ! La pi&egrave;ce fonctionne ind&eacute;pendamment, tandis que le jeton a une utilisation sp&eacute;cifique dans l&#39;&eacute;cosyst&egrave;me du projet, donc les deux ont leur propre r&ocirc;le et utilit&eacute;. Nous sommes une pi&egrave;ce index&eacute;e sur les actifs, qui est un diff&eacute;renciateur entre nous et la majorit&eacute; des crypto-monnaies existantes &agrave; l&#39;heure actuelle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>En una era de transformaciones tecnol&oacute;gicas en todos los niveles de nuestra vida cotidiana, estamos creando una soluci&oacute;n de contabilidad distribuida para resolver los problemas actuales de la mayor&iacute;a de los clientes y usuarios financieros. Al hacerlo, exploramos todas las soluciones posibles en el mercado en t&eacute;rminos de servicios financieros, tecnolog&iacute;as Blockchain, billetera bancaria y soluciones de seguridad para todas las transacciones y facilitamos las cosas a nuestros clientes y socios.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Siguiendo estudios detallados y siendo responsables de los asuntos financieros de nuestros clientes, as&iacute; como del crecimiento de la empresa y las necesidades de los clientes, creamos nuestra propia cadena de bloques, moneda, token y billetera digital que incorporar&aacute; m&uacute;ltiples cuentas bancarias (tanto Fiat como Crypto) , pensando en nuestras necesidades modernas. Cuando se trata de nuestras finanzas, todos queremos tener seguridad, transacciones r&aacute;pidas y pagar tarifas m&aacute;s bajas o ninguna de las que pagamos actualmente. Usamos la banca tradicional e incluso billeteras modernas, intercambios y soluciones de pago. Al tratar de lograr esto, el problema y la soluci&oacute;n se convirtieron en un desaf&iacute;o mayor, pero le complacer&aacute; saber que nunca abandonamos el desaf&iacute;o. Nuestro objetivo es construir algo que aborde la &quot;visi&oacute;n financiera y m&aacute;s all&aacute;&quot;. Nuestro mantra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cadena de bloques Flashmoni</p>\r\n\r\n<p>La forma m&aacute;s popular de lanzar nuestra DApp es en plataformas de cadena de bloques establecidas como Ethereum, BTC o EOS, etc., pero el problema es que cada cadena de bloques tiene compensaciones t&eacute;cnicas, cuellos de botella y restricciones. &iquest;Qu&eacute; sucede con una DApp que no puede funcionar debido a las limitaciones de la cadena de bloques que est&aacute; utilizando?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Las cadenas de bloques de Bitcoin y Ethereum ya est&aacute;n luchando para cumplir con el tr&aacute;fico, las velocidades de transacci&oacute;n, los tama&ntilde;os de bloque y el costo de la transacci&oacute;n. Por lo tanto, una vez m&aacute;s evaluamos la mayor&iacute;a de las cadenas de bloques relevantes populares en comparaci&oacute;n con nuestros requisitos. Las necesidades clave que ten&iacute;amos eran la escalabilidad, el costo de la transacci&oacute;n, la velocidad de la transacci&oacute;n, la seguridad, los precios estables, la eficiencia, los sistemas de recompensas, la estructura de datos y el algoritmo de consenso, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Entonces, nuestro objetivo era abordar c&oacute;mo varias de estas soluciones y aplicaciones existentes ser&iacute;an adecuadas para el ecosistema Flashmoni. En resumen, no fue suficiente para nosotros ni para nuestras necesidades clave objetivo, como se destac&oacute; anteriormente. Construir una cadena de bloques personalizada o bifurcar una actual podr&iacute;a ser una soluci&oacute;n a nuestro problema.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sin embargo, nadie conoce nuestro negocio mejor que nosotros, por lo que si construimos una cadena de bloques que se adapte espec&iacute;ficamente a nuestras necesidades, puede ayudarnos a ser m&aacute;s efectivos y eficientes en la gesti&oacute;n de nuestro negocio. Comenzamos este viaje y decidimos construir nuestra propia cadena de bloques por las siguientes razones:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Elecci&oacute;n del algoritmo de consenso</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Elecci&oacute;n del lenguaje de programaci&oacute;n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Control de c&oacute;digo base</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Posibilidad de actualizar c&oacute;mo y cuando quieras</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; M&aacute;xima flexibilidad y velocidad verdaderas a costos y tarifas muy reducidos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Estamos lanzando nuestra propia moneda, as&iacute; como nuestra propia moneda y plataforma de inversi&oacute;n. &iquest;Por qu&eacute;? &iexcl;Porque el ERC20 anterior era token y hay una gran diferencia entre Coin y Token! Coin opera de forma independiente, mientras que token tiene un uso espec&iacute;fico en el ecosistema del proyecto, por lo que ambos tienen su propio rol y utilidad. Somos una moneda vinculada a activos, que es un diferenciador entre nosotros y la mayor&iacute;a de las criptomonedas existentes en este momento.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'active', 'ozeety-the-flashmoni-blockchain-on-live-mode-soon', 'ozeety-the-flashmoni-blockchain-on-live-mode-soon', '2022-06-23 04:28:51', '2022-06-29 07:41:19'),
(54, 'An update from the Chairman and CEO', 'Une mise à jour du président-directeur général', 'Une mise à jour du président-directeur général', 'Une mise à jour du président-directeur général', 'https://lunar-estate.com/serge/admin-panel/upload/blog/1656572540-IMG_4530.JPG', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dear Community&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We have Breaking News!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We are pleased to announce a major milestone being reached. The first block on our Blockchain (&lt;a href=&quot;https://ozeety.com/index.html#about&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OZEETY&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;was mined successfully on 14th May 2019. This delivers yet another MVP and many to follow from our planned&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;roadmap. The next ones we are focused on are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flashwallet.io/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;FlashWallet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flashxchanger.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;- FlashXchanger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.oztcard.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OZTCARD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- FlashAdchain&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- FlashCryptostation&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- And many other value-added services being explored&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the above and more to follow, we will aim to achieve our vision of &amp;ldquo;Financial Inclusion and Beyond&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The full release of our version 1.0 MVP will be Q3-4, as the rest is more stress tested. It has been a long journey since 10th June 2018 and the end of our ICO fundraise. To say we had a few challenges is a bit of an understatement, however, we believe we are almost over the bad period of the downturn in the market, as well the delivery of the product. The delays made us even more focused on our detailed vision, as well as future product development roadmap. As you may all appreciate, this market moves very fast and our own change of platform development in the technology choices had to be adapted or we would have also become like an old dinosaur before we launched. Our constant reinvention and re-innovation mindset keep challenging us to future proof of our ongoing development to add value to the clients and investors. On that subject, we have now also recruited a full time more experienced CTO.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flashmoni.io/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Flashmoni Ecosystem&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our first consensus mechanism choice for our Blockchain (&lt;a href=&quot;https://flashxchanger.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OZEETY&lt;/a&gt;) was only, based on Proof-of-Stake (PoS).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This we found out later against the new Blockchain developers and advisors in the marketplace, riddled with fashion followers rather than business developers that PoS alone would not meet our total vision of a secure Omnichannel solution as fast as we were intended to.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;So we embarked on our relentless pursuit of the best solution and decided to develop a hybrid solution to further provide a better platform and comply with our community and the company desire for security, trust, scalability, etc. PoS is one of the best future consensuses but the method of deciding who can add new blocks and verify the current state of the blockchain has flaws just like the same process occur in POW, there is a lot of other consensuses out there like proof of elapsed time, proof of Authority, proof of capacity (aka space), proof of activity, proof of Burn but POW and now POS are at this time the most used consensus for blockchain development.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our Hybrid Solution gives the best of both consensus technologies and addresses the weakness in current technologies. By using PoW and PoS we also allow anonymous transactions. This combination of PoW and PoS consensus methodologies will be used until block 647999. Once that is achieved we will only use PoS consensus mechanism. We have also implemented the Quark algorithm because it&amp;rsquo;s a greener algorithm and allows for instant transactions, especially even small value transactions specifically aligned to our financial inclusion vision.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The benefits and advantages are numerous and include enhanced privacy, security, scalability, functionality, greener deployment, cheaper costs and speed of the transaction. All that is coupled with our gold pegged verified stable coin, which makes us the unique asset-pegged coin with such levels of privacy and security, giving peace of mind to our community. Our leitmotiv brings us to come up with a secure and anonymous solution where we are using a coin mixing technology that we call Obfuscation. That allows mixing of coins through the Master node network to make those amount of coin much harder to trace in the blockchain when you send it to someone else. It&amp;rsquo;s inherited from DASH. Private send is not really needed unless you want to anonymize your transactions. It&amp;rsquo;s not completely untraceable but makes it more difficult to track down the source and target address in this new world where privacy is a critical concern. Hence we thought that this feature will add value to our ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As we are willing to help the mainstream adoption of blockchain technology, we decided that for a certain category of transfer, a guaranteed zero confirmation of transactions is essential to speed transaction processing up and treat a large amount of them, whilst improving our blockchain adoption. We call this technology SwiftTX.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The technology achieves near-instant transaction confirmation (less than a second), while still overcoming double spend challenges. SwiftTX cost is 0.01&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ozeety.com/index.html#about&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OZTG&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and will give 5 confirmations in under 1 second. This feature has not been adopted by the wider cryptocurrency community.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Coin&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ozeety.com/index.html#about&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OZTG&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;will be in constant development to propose cutting edge Smart Contract and Daps, to allow people to create their own Tokens using our technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;For all the contributors who participate in our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.flashmoni.io/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ICO&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in 2018, the swap of their ERC20 tokens into&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ozeety.com/index.html#about&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OZTG&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Coin will be proceed on FlashXchanger and they will be notified for the registration process. But as almost all contributors already passed the KYC through the former version of the current FlashWallet, that process will be executed very quickly!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We have created a community on Bitcointalk and Telegram for the people willing to get involved in our development a little more active, so we invite you to join us. Also, weekly emails will be sent to our community to keep them posted.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A Big Thank You&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Once again, on behalf of myself, our new CEO Mru Patel and our whole new fully motivated growing team, our loyal community, investors and partners, without whom NONE of this would be possible for&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;such progress, Thank You!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Making our new vision of Financial Inclusion and Beyond Happen!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Best regards&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mru Patel / Partner and CEO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flashmoni.io/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Serge Maurice Lobr&amp;eacute;au / Founder, President &amp;amp; Chairman of FlashGroup&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '<p><strong>Dear Community</strong>,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have Breaking News!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are pleased to announce a major milestone being reached. The first block on our Blockchain (<a href=\"https://ozeety.com/index.html#about\" target=\"_blank\">OZEETY</a>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>was mined successfully on 14th May 2019. This delivers yet another MVP and many to follow from our planned</p>\r\n\r\n<p>roadmap. The next ones we are focused on are as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://flashwallet.io/\" target=\"_blank\">FlashWallet</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://flashxchanger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">- FlashXchanger</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.oztcard.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OZTCARD</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashAdchain</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashCryptostation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- And many other value-added services being explored</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the above and more to follow, we will aim to achieve our vision of &ldquo;Financial Inclusion and Beyond&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The full release of our version 1.0 MVP will be Q3-4, as the rest is more stress tested. It has been a long journey since 10th June 2018 and the end of our ICO fundraise. To say we had a few challenges is a bit of an understatement, however, we believe we are almost over the bad period of the downturn in the market, as well the delivery of the product. The delays made us even more focused on our detailed vision, as well as future product development roadmap. As you may all appreciate, this market moves very fast and our own change of platform development in the technology choices had to be adapted or we would have also become like an old dinosaur before we launched. Our constant reinvention and re-innovation mindset keep challenging us to future proof of our ongoing development to add value to the clients and investors. On that subject, we have now also recruited a full time more experienced CTO.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://flashmoni.io/\" target=\"_blank\">The Flashmoni Ecosystem</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our first consensus mechanism choice for our Blockchain (<a href=\"https://flashxchanger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OZEETY</a>) was only, based on Proof-of-Stake (PoS).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This we found out later against the new Blockchain developers and advisors in the marketplace, riddled with fashion followers rather than business developers that PoS alone would not meet our total vision of a secure Omnichannel solution as fast as we were intended to.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So we embarked on our relentless pursuit of the best solution and decided to develop a hybrid solution to further provide a better platform and comply with our community and the company desire for security, trust, scalability, etc. PoS is one of the best future consensuses but the method of deciding who can add new blocks and verify the current state of the blockchain has flaws just like the same process occur in POW, there is a lot of other consensuses out there like proof of elapsed time, proof of Authority, proof of capacity (aka space), proof of activity, proof of Burn but POW and now POS are at this time the most used consensus for blockchain development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Hybrid Solution gives the best of both consensus technologies and addresses the weakness in current technologies. By using PoW and PoS we also allow anonymous transactions. This combination of PoW and PoS consensus methodologies will be used until block 647999. Once that is achieved we will only use PoS consensus mechanism. We have also implemented the Quark algorithm because it&rsquo;s a greener algorithm and allows for instant transactions, especially even small value transactions specifically aligned to our financial inclusion vision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The benefits and advantages are numerous and include enhanced privacy, security, scalability, functionality, greener deployment, cheaper costs and speed of the transaction. All that is coupled with our gold pegged verified stable coin, which makes us the unique asset-pegged coin with such levels of privacy and security, giving peace of mind to our community. Our leitmotiv brings us to come up with a secure and anonymous solution where we are using a coin mixing technology that we call Obfuscation. That allows mixing of coins through the Master node network to make those amount of coin much harder to trace in the blockchain when you send it to someone else. It&rsquo;s inherited from DASH. Private send is not really needed unless you want to anonymize your transactions. It&rsquo;s not completely untraceable but makes it more difficult to track down the source and target address in this new world where privacy is a critical concern. Hence we thought that this feature will add value to our ecosystem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As we are willing to help the mainstream adoption of blockchain technology, we decided that for a certain category of transfer, a guaranteed zero confirmation of transactions is essential to speed transaction processing up and treat a large amount of them, whilst improving our blockchain adoption. We call this technology SwiftTX.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The technology achieves near-instant transaction confirmation (less than a second), while still overcoming double spend challenges. SwiftTX cost is 0.01&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ozeety.com/index.html#about\" target=\"_blank\">OZTG</a>&nbsp;and will give 5 confirmations in under 1 second. This feature has not been adopted by the wider cryptocurrency community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Coin&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ozeety.com/index.html#about\" target=\"_blank\">OZTG</a>&nbsp;will be in constant development to propose cutting edge Smart Contract and Daps, to allow people to create their own Tokens using our technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For all the contributors who participate in our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blog.flashmoni.io/\" target=\"_blank\">ICO</a>&nbsp;in 2018, the swap of their ERC20 tokens into&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ozeety.com/index.html#about\" target=\"_blank\">OZTG</a>&nbsp;Coin will be proceed on FlashXchanger and they will be notified for the registration process. But as almost all contributors already passed the KYC through the former version of the current FlashWallet, that process will be executed very quickly!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have created a community on Bitcointalk and Telegram for the people willing to get involved in our development a little more active, so we invite you to join us. Also, weekly emails will be sent to our community to keep them posted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Big Thank You</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once again, on behalf of myself, our new CEO Mru Patel and our whole new fully motivated growing team, our loyal community, investors and partners, without whom NONE of this would be possible for</p>\r\n\r\n<p>such progress, Thank You!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Making our new vision of Financial Inclusion and Beyond Happen!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best regards</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mru Patel / Partner and CEO</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://flashmoni.io/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Serge Maurice Lobr&eacute;au / Founder, President &amp; Chairman of FlashGroup</strong></a></p>\r\n', '<p><strong>Ch&egrave;re communaut&eacute;,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous avons des derni&egrave;res nouvelles !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous sommes heureux d&#39;annoncer qu&#39;une &eacute;tape importante a &eacute;t&eacute; franchie. Le premier bloc de notre Blockchain (OZEETY)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a &eacute;t&eacute; extrait avec succ&egrave;s le 14 mai 2019. Cela offre encore un autre MVP et beaucoup &agrave; suivre de notre plan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>feuille de route. Les suivants sur lesquels nous nous concentrons sont les suivants :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Portefeuille Flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashXchanger</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- OZTCARD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashAdchain</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashCryptostation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Et bien d&#39;autres services &agrave; valeur ajout&eacute;e en cours d&#39;exploration</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Avec ce qui pr&eacute;c&egrave;de et d&#39;autres &agrave; suivre, nous viserons &agrave; r&eacute;aliser notre vision de &quot;l&#39;inclusion financi&egrave;re et au-del&agrave;&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>La version compl&egrave;te de notre version 1.0 MVP sera Q3-4, car le reste est plus soumis &agrave; des tests de r&eacute;sistance. Ce fut un long voyage depuis le 10 juin 2018 et la fin de notre collecte de fonds ICO. Dire que nous avons eu quelques d&eacute;fis est un euph&eacute;misme, cependant, nous pensons que nous avons presque d&eacute;pass&eacute; la mauvaise p&eacute;riode du ralentissement du march&eacute;, ainsi que la livraison du produit. Les retards nous ont rendus encore plus concentr&eacute;s sur notre vision d&eacute;taill&eacute;e, ainsi que sur la future feuille de route de d&eacute;veloppement de produits. Comme vous pouvez tous l&#39;appr&eacute;cier, ce march&eacute; &eacute;volue tr&egrave;s rapidement et notre propre changement de plate-forme de d&eacute;veloppement dans les choix technologiques a d&ucirc; &ecirc;tre adapt&eacute;, sinon nous serions &eacute;galement devenus comme un vieux dinosaure avant de nous lancer. Notre &eacute;tat d&#39;esprit constant de r&eacute;invention et de r&eacute;innovation nous met au d&eacute;fi de prouver &agrave; l&#39;avenir notre d&eacute;veloppement continu pour ajouter de la valeur aux clients et aux investisseurs. Sur ce sujet, nous avons d&eacute;sormais &eacute;galement recrut&eacute; un CTO plus exp&eacute;riment&eacute; &agrave; temps plein.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&#39;&eacute;cosyst&egrave;me Flashmoni</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Notre premier choix de m&eacute;canisme de consensus pour notre Blockchain (OZEETY) &eacute;tait uniquement bas&eacute; sur la preuve de participation (PoS).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous avons d&eacute;couvert cela plus tard contre les nouveaux d&eacute;veloppeurs et conseillers Blockchain sur le march&eacute;, cribl&eacute;s d&#39;adeptes de la mode plut&ocirc;t que de d&eacute;veloppeurs commerciaux, que le PoS seul ne r&eacute;pondrait pas &agrave; notre vision totale d&#39;une solution omnicanale s&eacute;curis&eacute;e aussi rapidement que pr&eacute;vu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nous nous sommes donc lanc&eacute;s dans notre recherche incessante de la meilleure solution et avons d&eacute;cid&eacute; de d&eacute;velopper une solution hybride pour fournir une meilleure plate-forme et nous conformer aux d&eacute;sirs de notre communaut&eacute; et de l&#39;entreprise en mati&egrave;re de s&eacute;curit&eacute;, de confiance, d&#39;&eacute;volutivit&eacute;, etc. Le PoS est l&#39;un des meilleurs consensus futurs. mais la m&eacute;thode pour d&eacute;cider qui peut ajouter de nouveaux blocs et v&eacute;rifier l&#39;&eacute;tat actuel de la blockchain a des d&eacute;fauts tout comme le m&ecirc;me processus se produit dans POW, il y a beaucoup d&#39;autres consensus l&agrave;-bas comme la preuve du temps &eacute;coul&eacute;, la preuve de l&#39;autorit&eacute;, la preuve de capacit&eacute; (alias espace), preuve d&#39;activit&eacute;, preuve de Burn mais POW et maintenant POS sont &agrave; l&#39;heure actuelle le consensus le plus utilis&eacute; pour le d&eacute;veloppement de la blockchain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Notre solution hybride offre le meilleur des deux technologies consensuelles et r&eacute;pond aux faiblesses des technologies actuelles. En utilisant PoW et PoS, nous permettons &eacute;galement des transactions anonymes. Cette combinaison de m&eacute;thodologies de consensus PoW et PoS sera utilis&eacute;e jusqu&#39;au bloc 647999. Une fois que cela sera atteint, nous n&#39;utiliserons que le m&eacute;canisme de consensus PoS. Nous avons &eacute;galement mis en &oelig;uvre l&#39;algorithme Quark car il s&#39;agit d&#39;un algorithme plus &eacute;cologique et permet des transactions instantan&eacute;es, en particulier m&ecirc;me des transactions de petite valeur sp&eacute;cifiquement align&eacute;es sur notre vision de l&#39;inclusion financi&egrave;re.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les b&eacute;n&eacute;fices et les avantages sont nombreux et comprennent une confidentialit&eacute;, une s&eacute;curit&eacute;, une &eacute;volutivit&eacute;, des fonctionnalit&eacute;s, un d&eacute;ploiement plus &eacute;cologique, des co&ucirc;ts moins &eacute;lev&eacute;s et la rapidit&eacute; de la transaction. Tout cela est associ&eacute; &agrave; notre pi&egrave;ce stable v&eacute;rifi&eacute;e index&eacute;e sur l&#39;or, ce qui fait de nous l&#39;unique pi&egrave;ce index&eacute;e sur les actifs avec de tels niveaux de confidentialit&eacute; et de s&eacute;curit&eacute;, donnant la tranquillit&eacute; d&#39;esprit &agrave; notre communaut&eacute;. Notre leitmotiv nous am&egrave;ne &agrave; proposer une solution s&eacute;curis&eacute;e et anonyme o&ugrave; nous utilisons une technologie de m&eacute;lange de pi&egrave;ces que nous appelons Obfuscation. Cela permet de m&eacute;langer des pi&egrave;ces via le r&eacute;seau de n&oelig;uds ma&icirc;tres pour rendre cette quantit&eacute; de pi&egrave;ces beaucoup plus difficile &agrave; retracer dans la blockchain lorsque vous l&#39;envoyez &agrave; quelqu&#39;un d&#39;autre. Il est h&eacute;rit&eacute; de DASH. L&#39;envoi priv&eacute; n&#39;est pas vraiment n&eacute;cessaire, sauf si vous souhaitez anonymiser vos transactions. Ce n&#39;est pas compl&egrave;tement introuvable, mais il est plus difficile de retrouver l&#39;adresse source et cible dans ce nouveau monde o&ugrave; la confidentialit&eacute; est une pr&eacute;occupation essentielle. Nous avons donc pens&eacute; que cette fonctionnalit&eacute; ajouterait de la valeur &agrave; notre &eacute;cosyst&egrave;me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comme nous sommes dispos&eacute;s &agrave; aider &agrave; l&#39;adoption g&eacute;n&eacute;ralis&eacute;e de la technologie blockchain, nous avons d&eacute;cid&eacute; que pour une certaine cat&eacute;gorie de transfert, une confirmation z&eacute;ro garantie des transactions est essentielle pour acc&eacute;l&eacute;rer le traitement des transactions et en traiter un grand nombre, tout en am&eacute;liorant notre adoption de la blockchain. Nous appelons cette technologie SwiftTX.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>La technologie permet une confirmation de transaction quasi instantan&eacute;e (moins d&#39;une seconde), tout en surmontant les d&eacute;fis de la double d&eacute;pense. Le co&ucirc;t de SwiftTX est de 0,01 OZTG et donnera 5 confirmations en moins d&#39;une seconde. Cette fonctionnalit&eacute; n&#39;a pas &eacute;t&eacute; adopt&eacute;e par la communaut&eacute; des crypto-monnaies au sens large.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le Coin OZTG sera en d&eacute;veloppement constant pour proposer des contrats intelligents et des Daps de pointe, afin de permettre aux gens de cr&eacute;er leurs propres jetons en utilisant notre technologie.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pour tous les contributeurs qui participent &agrave; notre ICO en 2018, l&#39;&eacute;change de leurs tokens ERC20 en OZTG Coin se fera sur FlashXchanger et</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>Estimada comunidad,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&iexcl;Tenemos noticias de &uacute;ltima hora!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nos complace anunciar que se ha alcanzado un hito importante. El primer bloque en nuestra Blockchain (OZEETY)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>se extrajo con &eacute;xito el 14 de mayo de 2019. Esto ofrece otro MVP y muchos a seguir de nuestro plan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>mapa vial. Los siguientes en los que nos centramos son los siguientes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashWallet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashXchanger</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- TARJETA OZTC</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashAdchain</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- FlashCryptoestaci&oacute;n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Y muchos otros servicios de valor agregado que se est&aacute;n explorando</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Con lo anterior y m&aacute;s por seguir, nuestro objetivo ser&aacute; lograr nuestra visi&oacute;n de &quot;Inclusi&oacute;n financiera y m&aacute;s all&aacute;&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>El lanzamiento completo de nuestra versi&oacute;n 1.0 MVP ser&aacute; el tercer y cuarto trimestre, ya que el resto est&aacute; m&aacute;s sometido a pruebas de estr&eacute;s. Ha sido un largo viaje desde el 10 de junio de 2018 y el final de nuestra recaudaci&oacute;n de fondos de ICO. Decir que tuvimos algunos desaf&iacute;os es un poco insuficiente, sin embargo, creemos que casi hemos superado el mal per&iacute;odo de la recesi&oacute;n en el mercado, as&iacute; como la entrega del producto. Los retrasos hicieron que nos concentr&aacute;ramos a&uacute;n m&aacute;s en nuestra visi&oacute;n detallada, as&iacute; como en la hoja de ruta de desarrollo de productos futuros. Como todos pueden apreciar, este mercado se mueve muy r&aacute;pido y nuestro propio cambio de desarrollo de plataforma en las opciones de tecnolog&iacute;a tuvo que adaptarse o tambi&eacute;n nos habr&iacute;amos convertido en un viejo dinosaurio antes de lanzar. Nuestra mentalidad constante de reinvenci&oacute;n y reinnovaci&oacute;n nos sigue desafiando a la prueba futura de nuestro desarrollo continuo para agregar valor a los clientes e inversores. Sobre ese tema, ahora tambi&eacute;n hemos contratado a un CTO m&aacute;s experimentado a tiempo completo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>El ecosistema Flashmoni</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nuestra primera elecci&oacute;n de mecanismo de consenso para nuestra Blockchain (OZEETY) fue solo, basada en Prueba de participaci&oacute;n (PoS).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Esto lo descubrimos m&aacute;s tarde contra los nuevos desarrolladores y asesores de Blockchain en el mercado, plagado de seguidores de la moda en lugar de desarrolladores de negocios, que PoS por s&iacute; solo no cumplir&iacute;a con nuestra visi&oacute;n total de una soluci&oacute;n omnicanal segura tan r&aacute;pido como se pretend&iacute;a.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As&iacute; que nos embarcamos en nuestra b&uacute;squeda incesante de la mejor soluci&oacute;n y decidimos desarrollar una soluci&oacute;n h&iacute;brida para brindar una mejor plataforma y cumplir con nuestra comunidad y el deseo de seguridad, confianza, escalabilidad, etc. de la empresa. PoS es uno de los mejores consensos futuros. pero el m&eacute;todo para decidir qui&eacute;n puede agregar nuevos bloques y verificar el estado actual de la cadena de bloques tiene fallas al igual que el mismo proceso ocurre en POW, hay muchos otros consensos, como prueba de tiempo transcurrido, prueba de Autoridad, prueba de capacidad (tambi&eacute;n conocido como espacio), prueba de actividad, prueba de Burn pero POW y ahora POS son en este momento el consenso m&aacute;s utilizado para el desarrollo de blockchain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nuestra soluci&oacute;n h&iacute;brida ofrece lo mejor de ambas tecnolog&iacute;as de consenso y aborda la debilidad de las tecnolog&iacute;as actuales. Al usar PoW y PoS tambi&eacute;n permitimos transacciones an&oacute;nimas. Esta combinaci&oacute;n de metodolog&iacute;as de consenso PoW y PoS se usar&aacute; hasta el bloque 647999. Una vez que se logre, solo usaremos el mecanismo de consenso PoS. Tambi&eacute;n implementamos el algoritmo de Quark porque es un algoritmo m&aacute;s ecol&oacute;gico y permite transacciones instant&aacute;neas, especialmente incluso transacciones de peque&ntilde;o valor espec&iacute;ficamente alineadas con nuestra visi&oacute;n de inclusi&oacute;n financiera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Los beneficios y ventajas son numerosos e incluyen mayor privacidad, seguridad, escalabilidad, funcionalidad, implementaci&oacute;n m&aacute;s ecol&oacute;gica, costos m&aacute;s econ&oacute;micos y velocidad de transacci&oacute;n. Todo eso se combina con nuestra moneda estable verificada con vinculaci&oacute;n de oro, lo que nos convierte en la &uacute;nica moneda vinculada a activos con tales niveles de privacidad y seguridad, brindando tranquilidad a nuestra comunidad. Nuestro leitmotiv nos lleva a idear una soluci&oacute;n segura y an&oacute;nima donde estamos utilizando una tecnolog&iacute;a de mezcla de monedas que llamamos ofuscaci&oacute;n. Eso permite mezclar monedas a trav&eacute;s de la red de nodos maestros para hacer que esa cantidad de monedas sea mucho m&aacute;s dif&iacute;cil de rastrear en la cadena de bloques cuando se la env&iacute;a a otra persona. Se hereda de DASH. El env&iacute;o privado no es realmente necesario a menos que desee anonimizar sus transacciones. No es completamente imposible de rastrear, pero hace que sea m&aacute;s dif&iacute;cil rastrear la direcci&oacute;n de origen y de destino en este nuevo mundo donde la privacidad es una preocupaci&oacute;n cr&iacute;tica. Por lo tanto, pensamos que esta caracter&iacute;stica agregar&aacute; valor a nuestro ecosistema.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Como estamos dispuestos a ayudar a la adopci&oacute;n generalizada de la tecnolog&iacute;a blockchain, decidimos que para una determinada categor&iacute;a de transferencia, una confirmaci&oacute;n cero garantizada de las transacciones es esencial para acelerar el procesamiento de transacciones y tratar una gran cantidad de ellas, mientras mejoramos nuestra adopci&oacute;n blockchain. Llamamos a esta tecnolog&iacute;a SwiftTX.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>La tecnolog&iacute;a logra una confirmaci&oacute;n de transacci&oacute;n casi instant&aacute;nea (menos de un segundo), al tiempo que supera los desaf&iacute;os de doble gasto. El costo de SwiftTX es de 0.01 OZTG y dar&aacute; 5 confirmaciones en menos de 1 segundo. Esta caracter&iacute;stica no ha sido adoptada por la comunidad de criptomonedas en general.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coin OZTG estar&aacute; en constante desarrollo para proponer Smart Contract y Daps de vanguardia, para permitir que las personas creen sus propios Tokens utilizando nuestra tecnolog&iacute;a.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Para todos los contribuyentes que participan en nuestra ICO en 2018, el intercambio de sus tokens ERC20 en OZTG Coin se realizar&aacute; en FlashXchanger y</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'active', 'an-update-from-the-chairman-and-ceo', 'une-mise-à-jour-du-président-directeur-général', '2022-06-29 11:20:02', '2022-06-29 11:28:53');
INSERT INTO `sl_blogs` (`id`, `title`, `titlefr`, `titlesp`, `title_french`, `image`, `description`, `description_front`, `description_front_french`, `description_front_spanish`, `status`, `slug`, `slugfr`, `CreatedAt`, `UpdatedAt`) VALUES
(55, 'The crypto revolution and its effects Contrary to popular belief, cryptocurrencies were not invented', 'La révolution crypto et ses effets Contrairement aux idées reçues, les cryptomonnaies n\'ont pas été inventées', 'La cripto revolución y sus efectos Contrariamente a la creencia popular, las criptomonedas no fueron inventadas', 'La révolution crypto et ses effets Contrairement aux idées reçues, les cryptomonnaies n\'ont pas été inventées', 'https://lunar-estate.com/serge/admin-panel/upload/blog/1656572127-blog-2.JPG', '&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The crypto revolution and its effects&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Contrary to popular belief, cryptocurrencies were not invented to eradicate fiat currencies and banks. It&amp;rsquo;s entangled to traditional currencies, finance and payments channels that respond to certain inefficiencies. Thus, like the laws of the market, security, or regulation, the rules of the game are more or less the same and tend to become more uniform. Nevertheless, there are still some grey areas, particularly with regard to taxation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;In recent years, with the explosion of the number of crypto-currencies, new terms such as &amp;quot;HODL&amp;quot;, &amp;ldquo;REKT&amp;rdquo;,&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flashxchanger.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;BAGHOLDER&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo;,&amp;rdquo; SHILL&amp;rdquo; &amp;quot;When LAMBO ?&amp;quot; and others have appeared, symbolizing the revival of this market. At the same time, many people have become rich, sometimes overnight. I am thinking in particular of the peak of the main cryptocurrencies observed between the last quarter of 2017 and the first quarter of 2018, with Bitcoin reaching the historical price of &amp;euro;18,086.13 (Sat 16 Dec 2017, $19,665.00). With this coin alone, more than 22,000 people have become millionaires to date. All these newly rich people have found themselves with a new life but with new constraints, including fiscal ones.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The grey area of cryptocurrency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Let us be clear, there is to date no common policy for the taxation of gains/losses related to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ozeety.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;cryptocurrency.&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Governments prefer to leave this sector in the grey area. This in-between is problematic because, as in all situations where the contract is not clearly defined, each party tries to pull the quilt on its side. In this case, by playing with the tax system and therefore the state, this can be very risky if one is not perfectly advised. Many people do not realize how much the gains obtained via&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flashxchanger.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;exchangers&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and other products can have a critical impact on their professional and personal tax returns. It is therefore essential to know what you are getting into and what the repercussions of the actions you take will be.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As long as you stay in cryptocurrency, there is for the moment no substantial tax problem. But, as the use of these coins and tokens is not yet global, you will be obliged to return to a conventional currency one day or another. This is where the main problems begin.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Who has never been blocked by his bank after cashing in profits from&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ozblock.org/#/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Binance&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.flashmoni.io/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Kraken&lt;/a&gt;, or&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flashmoni.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Coinbase&lt;/a&gt;, to name but a few? You are then obliged to go to your branch, which is usually not crypto-friendly, for obvious reasons as its seen to be a threat to the fiat currency as well as traditional banking, to explain to them what is the source of the money. You could say that there are no clear rules and that you can do whatever you want with your money. Most of the time, depending on the level of income you receive from these exchanges, you will be asked to stop such transactions or you will simply be kicked out of your bank.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;From the bank&amp;#39;s point of view, Crypto companies are unregulated entities operating in an unregulated field where most of them are scams. As a former banker, I can assure you that this is the mental software deployed in banker&amp;#39;s minds.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAPIAN CAPITAL&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; offering today the banking of the future in a global economy&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As far as&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sapiancapital.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;SAPIAN CAPITAL&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;OTC (SCO) is concerned, we are firmly convinced that DLT (distributed ledger technology) will deeply change the perception and the way people will bank tomorrow. While we are not there yet, banks still have a big card to play in this new field that DLT has started to disrupt. Even if certain categories of the population will increasingly use monetary crypto-based services for all their daily transactions, such as remittance services, the banks will not collapse. They are just going to evolve as they always have, with the financial services market being big enough for both players. With over $ 7 Trillion in transactions on a daily basis, banks are the ones that control over 99% via fiat currencies with over 70% via the US Dollars. The benefits of digital currencies is slowly being realised by most major institutions including Goldman Sachs, JP Morgan and a number of others. Digital currencies are now being taken more seriously and even piloted via several governments including China, UK, India, Germany, France to name but a few.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Many companies and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flashxchanger.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;exchanges&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;now offer services related to this new asset class, ranging from the simple purchase of a coin to the development of a structured product such as a future, plus the implementation of leverage or margin calls. There is also a growing possibility of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.oztcard.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OTC transactions&lt;/a&gt;, which are vital for market liquidity and are intended more for a different user class of institutional owners and &amp;quot;Whales&amp;quot;. But here again, there is nothing about tax and asset optimization strategies in connection with crypto-asset.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '<h3><strong>The crypto revolution and its effects</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrary to popular belief, cryptocurrencies were not invented to eradicate fiat currencies and banks. It&rsquo;s entangled to traditional currencies, finance and payments channels that respond to certain inefficiencies. Thus, like the laws of the market, security, or regulation, the rules of the game are more or less the same and tend to become more uniform. Nevertheless, there are still some grey areas, particularly with regard to taxation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In recent years, with the explosion of the number of crypto-currencies, new terms such as &quot;HODL&quot;, &ldquo;REKT&rdquo;,&rdquo;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flashxchanger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">BAGHOLDER</a>&rdquo;,&rdquo; SHILL&rdquo; &quot;When LAMBO ?&quot; and others have appeared, symbolizing the revival of this market. At the same time, many people have become rich, sometimes overnight. I am thinking in particular of the peak of the main cryptocurrencies observed between the last quarter of 2017 and the first quarter of 2018, with Bitcoin reaching the historical price of &euro;18,086.13 (Sat 16 Dec 2017, $19,665.00). With this coin alone, more than 22,000 people have become millionaires to date. All these newly rich people have found themselves with a new life but with new constraints, including fiscal ones.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>The grey area of cryptocurrency</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Let us be clear, there is to date no common policy for the taxation of gains/losses related to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ozeety.com/\" target=\"_blank\">cryptocurrency.</a>&nbsp;Governments prefer to leave this sector in the grey area. This in-between is problematic because, as in all situations where the contract is not clearly defined, each party tries to pull the quilt on its side. In this case, by playing with the tax system and therefore the state, this can be very risky if one is not perfectly advised. Many people do not realize how much the gains obtained via&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flashxchanger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">exchangers</a>&nbsp;and other products can have a critical impact on their professional and personal tax returns. It is therefore essential to know what you are getting into and what the repercussions of the actions you take will be.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As long as you stay in cryptocurrency, there is for the moment no substantial tax problem. But, as the use of these coins and tokens is not yet global, you will be obliged to return to a conventional currency one day or another. This is where the main problems begin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who has never been blocked by his bank after cashing in profits from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ozblock.org/#/\" target=\"_blank\">Binance</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blog.flashmoni.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Kraken</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flashmoni.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Coinbase</a>, to name but a few? You are then obliged to go to your branch, which is usually not crypto-friendly, for obvious reasons as its seen to be a threat to the fiat currency as well as traditional banking, to explain to them what is the source of the money. You could say that there are no clear rules and that you can do whatever you want with your money. Most of the time, depending on the level of income you receive from these exchanges, you will be asked to stop such transactions or you will simply be kicked out of your bank.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From the bank&#39;s point of view, Crypto companies are unregulated entities operating in an unregulated field where most of them are scams. As a former banker, I can assure you that this is the mental software deployed in banker&#39;s minds.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>SAPIAN CAPITAL</strong> &ndash; offering today the banking of the future in a global economy</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As far as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sapiancapital.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SAPIAN CAPITAL</a>&nbsp;OTC (SCO) is concerned, we are firmly convinced that DLT (distributed ledger technology) will deeply change the perception and the way people will bank tomorrow. While we are not there yet, banks still have a big card to play in this new field that DLT has started to disrupt. Even if certain categories of the population will increasingly use monetary crypto-based services for all their daily transactions, such as remittance services, the banks will not collapse. They are just going to evolve as they always have, with the financial services market being big enough for both players. With over $ 7 Trillion in transactions on a daily basis, banks are the ones that control over 99% via fiat currencies with over 70% via the US Dollars. The benefits of digital currencies is slowly being realised by most major institutions including Goldman Sachs, JP Morgan and a number of others. Digital currencies are now being taken more seriously and even piloted via several governments including China, UK, India, Germany, France to name but a few.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many companies and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flashxchanger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">exchanges</a>&nbsp;now offer services related to this new asset class, ranging from the simple purchase of a coin to the development of a structured product such as a future, plus the implementation of leverage or margin calls. There is also a growing possibility of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.oztcard.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OTC transactions</a>, which are vital for market liquidity and are intended more for a different user class of institutional owners and &quot;Whales&quot;. But here again, there is nothing about tax and asset optimization strategies in connection with crypto-asset.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>La r&eacute;volution crypto et ses effets</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrairement &agrave; la croyance populaire, les crypto-monnaies n&#39;ont pas &eacute;t&eacute; invent&eacute;es pour &eacute;radiquer les monnaies fiduciaires et les banques. Il est emp&ecirc;tr&eacute; dans les monnaies traditionnelles, les canaux de financement et de paiement qui r&eacute;pondent &agrave; certaines inefficacit&eacute;s. Ainsi, comme les lois du march&eacute;, de la s&eacute;curit&eacute; ou de la r&eacute;gulation, les r&egrave;gles du jeu sont plus ou moins les m&ecirc;mes et tendent &agrave; s&#39;uniformiser. N&eacute;anmoins, des zones d&#39;ombre subsistent, notamment en mati&egrave;re de fiscalit&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ces derni&egrave;res ann&eacute;es, avec l&#39;explosion du nombre de crypto-monnaies, de nouveaux termes tels que &quot;HODL&quot;, &quot;REKT&quot;, &quot;BAGHOLDER&quot;, &quot;SHILL&quot; &quot;Quand LAMBO ?&quot; et d&#39;autres sont apparus, symbolisant le renouveau de ce march&eacute;. Dans le m&ecirc;me temps, de nombreuses personnes sont devenues riches, parfois du jour au lendemain. Je pense notamment au pic des principales crypto-monnaies observ&eacute; entre le dernier trimestre 2017 et le premier trimestre 2018, le Bitcoin atteignant le prix historique de 18 086,13 &euro; (sam 16 d&eacute;c 2017, 19 665,00 $). Avec cette seule pi&egrave;ce, plus de 22 000 personnes sont devenues millionnaires &agrave; ce jour. Tous ces nouveaux riches se sont retrouv&eacute;s avec une nouvelle vie mais avec de nouvelles contraintes, notamment fiscales.<br />\r\nLa zone grise de la crypto-monnaie</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Soyons clairs, il n&#39;existe &agrave; ce jour aucune politique commune de taxation des gains/pertes li&eacute;s &agrave; la crypto-monnaie. Les gouvernements pr&eacute;f&egrave;rent laisser ce secteur dans la zone grise. Cet entre-deux est probl&eacute;matique car, comme dans toutes les situations o&ugrave; le contrat n&#39;est pas clairement d&eacute;fini, chaque partie essaie de tirer la couette de son c&ocirc;t&eacute;. Dans ce cas, en jouant avec la fiscalit&eacute; et donc l&#39;&eacute;tat, cela peut &ecirc;tre tr&egrave;s risqu&eacute; si l&#39;on n&#39;est pas parfaitement conseill&eacute;. Nombreux sont ceux qui ne se rendent pas compte &agrave; quel point les gains obtenus via les &eacute;changeurs et autres produits peuvent avoir un impact critique sur leurs d&eacute;clarations fiscales professionnelles et personnelles. Il est donc essentiel de savoir dans quoi vous vous embarquez et quelles seront les r&eacute;percussions des actions que vous posez.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tant que vous restez dans la crypto-monnaie, il n&#39;y a pour l&#39;instant pas de probl&egrave;me fiscal substantiel. Mais, comme l&#39;utilisation de ces pi&egrave;ces et jetons n&#39;est pas encore mondiale, vous serez oblig&eacute; de revenir un jour ou l&#39;autre &agrave; une monnaie conventionnelle. C&#39;est l&agrave; que commencent les principaux probl&egrave;mes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qui n&#39;a jamais &eacute;t&eacute; bloqu&eacute; par sa banque apr&egrave;s avoir encaiss&eacute; les b&eacute;n&eacute;fices de Binance, Kraken ou Coinbase, pour ne citer qu&#39;eux ? Vous &ecirc;tes alors oblig&eacute; de vous rendre dans votre agence, qui n&#39;est g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement pas crypto-friendly, pour des raisons &eacute;videntes car elle est consid&eacute;r&eacute;e comme une menace pour la monnaie fiduciaire ainsi que pour les banques traditionnelles, pour leur expliquer quelle est la source de l&#39;argent. Vous pourriez dire qu&#39;il n&#39;y a pas de r&egrave;gles claires et que vous pouvez faire ce que vous voulez avec votre argent. La plupart du temps, selon le niveau de revenus que vous recevez de ces &eacute;changes, il vous sera demand&eacute; d&#39;arr&ecirc;ter ces transactions ou vous serez simplement expuls&eacute; de votre banque.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du point de vue de la banque, les soci&eacute;t&eacute;s Crypto sont des entit&eacute;s non r&eacute;glement&eacute;es op&eacute;rant dans un domaine non r&eacute;glement&eacute; o&ugrave; la plupart d&#39;entre elles sont des escroqueries. En tant qu&#39;ancien banquier, je peux vous assurer que c&#39;est le logiciel mental d&eacute;ploy&eacute; dans l&#39;esprit des banquiers.<br />\r\nSAPIAN CAPITAL &ndash; offrir aujourd&#39;hui la banque du futur dans une &eacute;conomie mondiale</p>\r\n\r\n<p>En ce qui concerne SAPIAN CAPITAL OTC (SCO), nous sommes fermement convaincus que la DLT (Distributed Ledger Technology) va profond&eacute;ment changer la perception et la fa&ccedil;on dont les gens vont banquer demain. Si nous n&#39;en sommes pas encore l&agrave;, les banques ont encore une grosse carte &agrave; jouer dans ce nouveau domaine que le DLT a commenc&eacute; &agrave; bousculer. M&ecirc;me si certaines cat&eacute;gories de la population utiliseront de plus en plus les services mon&eacute;taires bas&eacute;s sur la cryptographie pour toutes leurs transactions quotidiennes, comme les services de transfert de fonds, les banques ne s&#39;effondreront pas. Ils vont simplement &eacute;voluer comme ils l&#39;ont toujours fait, le march&eacute; des services financiers &eacute;tant suffisamment grand pour les deux acteurs. Avec plus de 7 000 milliards de dollars de transactions au quotidien, ce sont les banques qui contr&ocirc;lent plus de 99% via les monnaies fiduciaires avec plus de 70% via le dollar am&eacute;ricain. Les avantages des monnaies num&eacute;riques sont lentement r&eacute;alis&eacute;s par la plupart des grandes institutions, notamment Goldman Sachs, JP Morgan et un certain nombre d&#39;autres. Les monnaies num&eacute;riques sont d&eacute;sormais prises plus au s&eacute;rieux et m&ecirc;me pilot&eacute;es par plusieurs gouvernements, dont la Chine, le Royaume-Uni, l&#39;Inde, l&#39;Allemagne, la France, pour n&#39;en citer que quelques-uns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nDe nombreuses entreprises et bourses proposent d&eacute;sormais des services li&eacute;s &agrave; cette nouvelle classe d&#39;actifs, allant du simple achat d&#39;un coin au d&eacute;veloppement d&#39;un produit structur&eacute; tel qu&#39;un future, en passant par la mise en place d&#39;effets de levier ou d&#39;appels de marge. Il existe &eacute;galement une possibilit&eacute; croissante de transactions de gr&eacute; &agrave; gr&eacute;, qui sont vitales pour la liquidit&eacute; du march&eacute; et s&#39;adressent davantage &agrave; une classe d&#39;utilisateurs diff&eacute;rente de propri&eacute;taires institutionnels et de &quot;baleines&quot;. Mais l&agrave; encore, il n&#39;y a rien sur les strat&eacute;gies fiscales et d&#39;optimisation patrimoniale en lien avec les crypto-actifs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>La cripto revoluci&oacute;n y sus efectos</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contrariamente a la creencia popular, las criptomonedas no se inventaron para erradicar las monedas fiduciarias y los bancos. Est&aacute; enredado con las monedas tradicionales, las finanzas y los canales de pago que responden a ciertas ineficiencias. As&iacute;, al igual que las leyes del mercado, la seguridad o la regulaci&oacute;n, las reglas del juego son m&aacute;s o menos las mismas y tienden a uniformarse. Sin embargo, todav&iacute;a existen algunas &aacute;reas grises, particularmente en lo que respecta a la fiscalidad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>En los &uacute;ltimos a&ntilde;os, con la explosi&oacute;n del n&uacute;mero de criptomonedas, nuevos t&eacute;rminos como &quot;HODL&quot;, &quot;REKT&quot;, &quot;BAGHOLDER&quot;, &quot;SHILL&quot; &quot;&iquest;Cu&aacute;ndo LAMBO?&quot; y han aparecido otros, que simbolizan la reactivaci&oacute;n de este mercado. Al mismo tiempo, muchas personas se han hecho ricas, a veces de la noche a la ma&ntilde;ana. Estoy pensando en particular en el pico de las principales criptomonedas observado entre el &uacute;ltimo trimestre de 2017 y el primer trimestre de 2018, con Bitcoin alcanzando el precio hist&oacute;rico de 18 086,13 &euro; (s&aacute;bado 16 dic 2017, 19 665,00 $). Solo con esta moneda, m&aacute;s de 22.000 personas se han convertido en millonarias hasta la fecha. Todos estos nuevos ricos se han encontrado con una nueva vida pero con nuevas limitaciones, incluidas las fiscales.<br />\r\nEl &aacute;rea gris de las criptomonedas</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Seamos claros, hasta la fecha no existe una pol&iacute;tica com&uacute;n para la tributaci&oacute;n de las ganancias/p&eacute;rdidas relacionadas con las criptomonedas. Los gobiernos prefieren dejar este sector en la zona gris. Este intermedio es problem&aacute;tico porque, como en todas las situaciones en las que el contrato no est&aacute; claramente definido, cada parte trata de poner el edred&oacute;n de lado. En este caso, jugar con el sistema fiscal y por ende con el estado puede ser muy arriesgado si no se est&aacute; perfectamente asesorado. Muchas personas no se dan cuenta de cu&aacute;nto pueden tener un impacto cr&iacute;tico en sus declaraciones de impuestos profesionales y personales las ganancias obtenidas a trav&eacute;s de los intercambiadores y otros productos. Por ello, es fundamental saber en qu&eacute; te est&aacute;s metiendo y cu&aacute;les ser&aacute;n las repercusiones de las acciones que realices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mientras permanezca en la criptomoneda, por el momento no hay un problema fiscal sustancial. Pero, como el uso de estas monedas y tokens a&uacute;n no es global, te ver&aacute;s obligado a volver a una moneda convencional un d&iacute;a u otro. Aqu&iacute; es donde comienzan los principales problemas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&iquest;Qui&eacute;n nunca ha sido bloqueado por su banco despu&eacute;s de cobrar ganancias de Binance, Kraken o Coinbase, por nombrar solo algunos? Luego, est&aacute; obligado a ir a su sucursal, que generalmente no es compatible con criptograf&iacute;a, por razones obvias, ya que se considera una amenaza para la moneda fiduciaria y la banca tradicional, para explicarles cu&aacute;l es la fuente del dinero. Se podr&iacute;a decir que no hay reglas claras y que puedes hacer lo que quieras con tu dinero. La mayor&iacute;a de las veces, dependiendo del nivel de ingresos que reciba de estos intercambios, se le pedir&aacute; que detenga dichas transacciones o simplemente lo echar&aacute;n de su banco.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Desde el punto de vista del banco, las empresas de criptomonedas son entidades no reguladas que operan en un campo no regulado donde la mayor&iacute;a de ellas son estafas. Como antiguo banquero, puedo asegurarles que este es el software mental desplegado en la mente de los banqueros.<br />\r\nSAPIAN CAPITAL: ofreciendo hoy la banca del futuro en una econom&iacute;a global</p>\r\n\r\n<p>En lo que respecta a SAPIAN CAPITAL OTC (SCO), estamos firmemente convencidos de que DLT (tecnolog&iacute;a de contabilidad distribuida) cambiar&aacute; profundamente la percepci&oacute;n y la forma en que las personas realizar&aacute;n operaciones bancarias ma&ntilde;ana. Si bien a&uacute;n no hemos llegado all&iacute;, los bancos todav&iacute;a tienen una gran carta que jugar en este nuevo campo que DLT ha comenzado a interrumpir. Incluso si ciertas categor&iacute;as de la poblaci&oacute;n utilizaran cada vez m&aacute;s los servicios criptogr&aacute;ficos monetarios para todas sus transacciones diarias, como los servicios de remesas, los bancos no colapsar&aacute;n. Simplemente van a evolucionar como siempre lo han hecho, y el mercado de servicios financieros ser&aacute; lo suficientemente grande para ambos jugadores. Con m&aacute;s de $ 7 billones en transacciones diarias, los bancos son los que controlan m&aacute;s del 99% a trav&eacute;s de monedas fiduciarias con m&aacute;s del 70% a trav&eacute;s de d&oacute;lares estadounidenses. La mayor&iacute;a de las principales instituciones, incluidas Goldman Sachs, JP Morgan y muchas otras, se est&aacute;n dando cuenta lentamente de los beneficios de las monedas digitales. Las monedas digitales ahora se toman m&aacute;s en serio e incluso se ponen a prueba a trav&eacute;s de varios gobiernos, incluidos China, Reino Unido, India, Alemania, Francia, por nombrar solo algunos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nMuchas empresas y bolsas ahora ofrecen servicios relacionados con esta nueva clase de activos, que van desde la simple compra de una moneda hasta el desarrollo de un producto estructurado como un futuro, adem&aacute;s de la implementaci&oacute;n de llamadas de margen o apalancamiento. Tambi&eacute;n existe una posibilidad creciente de transacciones OTC, que son vitales para la liquidez del mercado y est&aacute;n destinadas m&aacute;s a una clase diferente de usuarios de propietarios institucionales y &quot;Ballenas&quot;. Pero aqu&iacute; nuevamente, no hay nada sobre estrategias de optimizaci&oacute;n de impuestos y activos en relaci&oacute;n con los criptoactivos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'active', 'the-crypto-revolution-and-its-effects-contrary-to-popular-belief-cryptocurrencies-were-not-invented', 'the-crypto-revolution-and-its-effects-contrary-to-...', '2022-06-29 11:46:22', NULL);

